ENGLISH: The Train sector of the China Set of OpenTTD.
Locomotives, MUs, Coaches and Wagons in China Mainland. More contents in the future.
SIMPLIFIED CHINESE: 中国大陆的火车，包括机车、动车组、车厢。未来会有更多内容。{RED}在游戏中更新NewGRF时请注意最低兼容版本！请不要强行更新！

ENGLISH: Adjust vehicle loading speed. Default is 100%.
SIMPLIFIED CHINESE: 调整车辆装载速度。默认为100%。

ENGLISH: Adjust vehicle purchase costs. Default is 25%.
SIMPLIFIED CHINESE: 调整车辆购买费用。默认为25%。

ENGLISH: Adjust vehicle running costs. Default is 25%.
SIMPLIFIED CHINESE: 调整车辆运营费用。默认为25%。

ENGLISH: Adjust cargo age period (the ability of keeping freshness of cargo and comfort for passengers) of coaches and wagons. Default is 100%. Cargo age period varies, so that a passenger would usually pay more for their long journey in a soft sleeper coach than in a hard seat coach.
SIMPLIFIED CHINESE: 调整车厢的货物贬值周期（旅客舒适度/货物保鲜度）。默认为100%。货物贬值周期随车厢种类而有不同；长途乘客使用软卧时一般会较使用硬座时付更多的钱。

ENGLISH: Type 25 Passenger Coaches built after 2014 are {DKGREEN}"Gaozu Green"{BLACK} by default
SIMPLIFIED CHINESE: 2014年后建造的25型客车默认刷{DKGREEN}绿

ENGLISH: Choose whether to print{DKGREEN} Canarium Green (also called "Gaozu Green"){BLACK} to Type 25 Passenger Coaches built after 2014 by default
SIMPLIFIED CHINESE: 决定2014年后建造的25型客车是否默认刷{DKGREEN}绿

ENGLISH: Cargo age period of mail and freight wagons
SIMPLIFIED CHINESE: 单独设置货车的货物贬值周期

ENGLISH: Set cargo age period of mail and freight wagons individually, multiplied by "Cargo Age Period" again. It makes very-long-distance transport of freight possible.
SIMPLIFIED CHINESE: 单独设置邮件车和货车的货物贬值周期，在选项"货物贬值周期"上叠加计算。这个选项使超长途货物运输成为可能

SIMPLIFIED CHINESE: 请切换至控制台模式，键入 "set dynamic_engines 1"， 否则您无法游玩中国包。
